351
00:33:16.467 --> 00:33:18.093
Why didn't you tell me?

352
00:33:18.177 --> 00:33:21.429
I didn't think
there was anything wrong with it.


353
00:33:27.103 --> 00:33:29.729
Of all the children, 
Donald Miller.

354
00:33:31.524 --> 00:33:32.899
I suppose it makes sense.

355
00:33:32.984 --> 00:33:36.153
