00:40:25.104 --> 00:40:26.854
No, I've already had my cup.

434
00:40:26.939 --> 00:40:30.441
- Is there sugar?
- Sugar?


435
00:40:32.570 --> 00:40:39.117
Yes, yes. Somewhere here.

436
00:40:40.786 --> 00:40:45.081
