Never remembered to take it out.


437
00:40:45.165 --> 00:40:47.166
It mustn't have been much
to give up, then.


438
00:40:49.795 --> 00:40:52.714
I'm sure you're right.
Here it is.


439
00:40:52.798 --> 00:40:59.429
I'll serve you, although
for want of practice I'm a little clumsy.


440
00:41:01.307 --> 00:41:06.144
- I see your fingernails.
- Wear them a little long.


441
00:41:07.813 --> 00:41:09.522
- The sugar?
- Yes. One?


442
00:41:09.607 --> 00:41:10.815
Three.

443
00:41:11.817 --> 00:41:13.735
- Three?
- Sweet tooth.


444
00:41:14.236 --> 00:41:17.280
Two. Three.

445
00:41:18.365 --> 00:41:21.492
- Sister, you care for sugar?
- Never.


446
00:41:21.577 --> 00:41:24.579
Not that there's
anything wrong with sugar.


447
00:41:25.998 --> 00:41:28.833
Well, thank you, Father,
for making time for us.


