476
00:42:59.800 --> 00:43:03.177
Oh, nothing. It's an idea for a sermon.

477
00:43:03.595 --> 00:43:07.265
- Oh. You had one right now?
- I get them all the time.


478
00:43:07.641 --> 00:43:09.142
How fortunate.

479
00:43:09.226 --> 00:43:11.644
I forget them,
so I have to write them down.


480
00:43:13.230 --> 00:43:14.939
What is the idea?

481
00:43:17.067 --> 00:43:18.526
Intolerance.

482
00:43:24.450 --> 00:43:25.867
Would you like
a little more tea, Father?


483
00:43:25.951 --> 00:43:27.285
Not yet.

